data.description: Across from Ryan Place Park, this wonderful home awaits. A very large covered front porch welcomes you and guests. Picture yourself here reading, drinking coffee or a nice glass of wine at the end of the day. Classic Ryan Place Charm with hardwood floors, you have 2 bedrooms downstairs and a large loft bedroom with full bath upstairs. The detach two car garage is oversized and has extra space for a work shop. This is a rare find in the area. Come see for yourself and make this Ryan Place Charmer your own. Buyer backed out, not sure why as we did not get an inspection report.  Seller has had foundation work done late October.
